{"tid":2254342,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"咁嘅情況，應該係箍牙定係矯骨？","createTime":"2020-10-22T18:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T02:33:25.000Z","uid":375312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"049bac4ef43353056dbe449d545e5ec56fe49288","tid":2254342,"uid":375312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T18:01:11.000Z","msg":"小弟由細到大食嘢都係用右邊牙咬，搞到啲牙同骨都有少少移位。<br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjKEcGF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjKEcGF.png&h=81e26991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概就係下顎骨偏去左邊少少，當我合返正個骨位，但係啲牙齒就又黐唔實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲搞到左下嘴唇同下巴唔太平均，雖然平時睇就唔係好明顯，但係我一影相就見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打知要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e275bf7350379be0c47c2fed481d8fd46befd9bd","tid":2254342,"uid":336214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T18:02:36.000Z","msg":"問牙醫"},{"pid":"36841ff264c48b968ef744255bff53ee329de7c2","tid":2254342,"uid":368597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T18:04:44.000Z","msg":"之後食嘢用返左邊 其實我都係咁 之前去睇過個正骨發現咗我有呢個問題 叫我多啲用返左邊咬同用手按下左邊面 但一按就痛到仆晒街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b4cc9a2d72a3cb02aa8649c813ce69d18770b6","tid":2254342,"uid":375312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e275bf7350379be0c47c2fed481d8fd46befd9bd","tid":2254342,"uid":336214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T18:02:36.000Z","msg":"問牙醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T18:05:26.000Z","msg":"Ok!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85e6be1801243c29d4d6763dc7a92c7d8c96479","tid":2254342,"uid":375312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36841ff264c48b968ef744255bff53ee329de7c2",